OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FSinn Fein has launched a series of
OL,8,Fproposed reforms aimed at "removing
OL,9,Fthe ever-present threat of collapse"
OL,10,Fat Stormont.
OL,12,FThe largest party in the Assembly is
OL,13,Fthe latest to publish a reform
OL,14,Fdocument aimed at stabilising the
OL,15,Finstitutions, which have experienced
OL,16,Fsignificant turbulence in recent years
OL,17,Fand effective collapses between 2017
OL,18,Fand 2020 and 2022 to 2024.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
