FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FLaunching the proposals at Stormont on
OL,8,FMonday, First Minister and Sinn Fein
OL,9,Fvice president Michelle O'Neill
OL,10,Frestated the party's preference for a
OL,11,Funited Ireland, but said their
OL,12,FBuilding Better Politics document was
OL,13,Fa bid to improve the operations of the
OL,14,Fcurrent institutions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
