CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FThe eight-page document includes
OL,8,Fproposals for reform designed to
OL,9,Fensure the Assembly and Executive can
OL,10,Fcontinue to function during a
OL,11,Fpolitical crisis, and prevent any
OL,12,Fsingle party being able to "block or
OL,13,Fcollapse" the institutions.
OL,26,@tD@\OUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FWhile Sinn Fein is proposing that the
OL,8,Flargest nationalist party and the
OL,9,Flargest unionist party should retain
OL,10,Fthe right to nominate the first
OL,11,Fminister and deputy first minister, if
OL,12,Feither chooses not to nominate, that
OL,13,Fopportunity would pass to other
OL,14,Fparties.
OL,16,FThe party is also proposing the
OL,17,Fremoval of the "veto" over the
OL,18,Felection of the Stormont speaker at
OL,19,Fthe first meeting of a new assembly,
OL,20,Fensuring no potential blockage for the
OL,21,FAssembly starting its work.
OL,26,@yD@POUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FIn addition, there is a proposal to
OL,8,Fexplore options to "introduce greater
OL,9,Ftransparency and accountability in
OL,10,Frelation to decisions made by the
OL,11,Fspeaker".
OL,13,FOther proposals include devolving
OL,14,Ffiscal powers, equality for MLAs who
OL,15,Fare designated as "other", instead of
OL,16,Funionist or nationalist, and
OL,17,F"normalising" the appointment of the
OL,18,Fjustice minister.
OL,26,@pD@TOUsD@HO]wD@SOUwD@YO]yD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
