CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FThe document comes after proposals for
OL,8,Freform of the institutions previously
OL,9,Fpublished by the Alliance Party as
OL,10,Fwell as the SDLP, which leads the
OL,11,Fofficial Opposition at Stormont.
OL,13,FMs O'Neill said the current set-up,
OL,14,Fworking in a "forced coalition" with
OL,15,Fparties which had "very different
OL,16,Fpolitics", made for a "challenging and
OL,17,Fdifficult arrangement".
OL,26,@vD@NOUvD@_O]wD@SOUxD@IO]xD@WOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,F"I think our unusual, and some might
OL,8,Falso say abnormal, political
OL,9,Finfrastructure are the necessary
OL,10,Fproduct of the peace process and
OL,11,Ftherefore we are committed to being
OL,12,Fhere, to working every day, to try to
OL,13,Fdeliver for people despite all those
OL,14,Fchallenges," she said.
OL,16,F"But we do believe that we can make
OL,17,Fchanges that improve how we do
OL,18,Fgovernment, that we can do without
OL,19,Fundermining the core principles of the
OL,20,FGood Friday Agreement.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@LO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,F"So today, this is about our
OL,8,Fcontribution to the ongoing debate.
OL,9,FIt's an important piece of work and
OL,10,Fwe're presenting our considered
OL,11,Fproposals on reform, that we believe
OL,12,Fwill make a difference to the
OL,13,Fpolitical institutions."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FShe said: "Principally, we are
OL,8,Fproposing to remove the ever-present
OL,9,Fthreat of collapse, because this is
OL,10,Fsomething that frequently is raised,
OL,11,Fbecause the greatest obstacle to
OL,12,Fdelivery is when the institutions are
OL,13,Fprevented from operating themselves,
OL,14,Fso removing the veto of the largest
OL,15,Fparties over the operation of the
OL,16,FExecutive and Assembly is therefore
OL,17,Fthe primary proposal we are
OL,18,Fadvocating."
OL,26,@oD@KOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FMs O'Neill said other proposals in the
OL,8,Fdocument were aimed at improving
OL,9,Ftransparency, accountability,
OL,10,Fdemocracy and delivery.
OL,12,F"We do recognise that these proposals
OL,13,Falone will not resolve every challenge
OL,14,Fthat we have, and the reason that I
OL,15,Fsay that is that reform won't overcome
OL,16,Fthe reality that there are those who
OL,17,Fsimply don't want to share power," she
OL,18,Fsaid, highlighting the DUP.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FMeanwhile, DUP leader Gavin Robinson
OL,8,Fsaid he would read the proposals with
OL,9,Finterest, but that he wanted to see a
OL,10,Freform of how parties engaged.
OL,12,F"One thing that needs to happen in
OL,13,Fthis place is reforming of the heart
OL,14,Fand how people are willing to engage
OL,15,Fwith each other, and whether they're
OL,16,Finterested in making this place work
OL,17,For not," he told media in the Great
OL,18,FHall at Stormont.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
