CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780413074
OL,3,CSinn Fein proposals aim to 'remove
OL,4,Cever-present threat of collapse' at
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,F"The structures, the procedures, the
OL,8,Finstitutions ` that doesn't matter,
OL,9,Fwhatever they are, if someone is
OL,10,Fcoming at it with the wrong approach,
OL,11,Fit isn't going to work."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]
